heavyfood<-fastfood_calories %>%
  mutate(heavy_food = case_when(calories>= 500~"heavy",

#Display the data vis of total fat per each type of restaurant

fastfood_calories %>%
  group_by(restaurant) %>%
  summarise(totalfat = sum(total_fat)) %>%
  arrange(desc(totalfat)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  ggplot(aes(restaurant, totalfat, fill=restaurant)) +
  geom_col() +
  coord_flip() +
  labs(x="Restaurant", y="Total fat of restaurant", title="Total fat for each type of restaurant")
